cal comprehensive interpretation of gamma-ray data and its\npresent unexplained features. Model parameters are provided, which supply a\nmore realistic basis for high-energy gamma-ray studies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 Jan 2019 19:00:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-28"}
