le of enlarging the size of the residuals to roughly 0.2\nmas.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 25 Jan 2019 15:02:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 8 Feb 2019 14:54:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-20"}
